name: The Fool
description: Marionette. Digitally altered ink on paper. Part of the "Plague Pigeon" series featured at the solo show "Midnight Cowboy" by Gunnar Magnus. Midnight Cowboy is a dark reflection of the new world burgeoning forth from the pandemic. See the show until May 15 at Port Authority Bus Terminal. This NFT will have a hand in cementing the historical significance of this show, it's location, and subject matter, for all time.
